Don't mind the spelling. Had to write fast.

* Iron Raptor simply watches as Shadow moves up and out of her range, almost 
wishing that she knew how to use those two wings which were nestled inside 
of her back.
But she couldn't and so far the sword was all she knew of the weapons she 
carried.
But seeing the grenade she didn't panic, already knowing that Prowl was on 
it. Watching the explosion in the air instead of at her feet.
Her sword arem relaxing until the tip of the blade came to rest on the 
ground, her eyes still on the sky.*

< I'm fine.>

* She answered, still looking towards the retreating Shadow as he moved on.
So much for testing her body out. There was still so much she didn't know 
about it.
Iron Raptor lowered her head from the clouds and turned it towards Prowl as 
he walked up to her, simply looking at him through the slits of her visor on 
her helm, seeing Firearm pull up and then transform.
Did he even recognize her? Probably.
Iron Raptor gave Firearm an absentminded wave before turning her attentions 
back towrds Prowl.*

< Why did Kluster call a meeting, is it because of the threat from the 
Predacons of attack?>

* She was ready to go, yes. But she wanted a few questions answered first.*
